HowToGetDescription.SourceString: Can randomly be found in the marketplace or by beating levels.
HowToGetDescription.LocalizedString: Can randomly be found in the marketplace or by beating levels.

Description.SourceString: Dungeon Key. Grants access to the Waterfall Valley. Known both for its resplendent beauty, and those who vanished in search of its secrets. There is no failure penalty, nor partial completion rewards.
